\fs44  2 C. black pepper infused Vodka\
 4 C. tomato juice, unseasoned and preferably organic\
 1 lemon, juiced\
 1 T. Worcestershire\
 5-10 drops hot sauce (do this last to taste)\
 3 T. celery salt (or 1.5 Tbsp salt and 1.5 Tbsp ground celery seed)\
 2 T. freshly grated horseradish\
 celery stalks for garnish\
\
In a large pitcher, add vodka, tomato juice, lemon juice, Worcestershire, celery salt, and horseradish. Taste and add hot sauce if desired. Garnish with celery stalks.\
